<span id="xi.i-p7"></span>**3.** Arundinem quassatam non perfringet, nec
linum fumans extinguet; in veritate proferet judicium.

<span id="xi.i-p8"></span>**4.** He shall not fail nor be discouraged,
till he have set judgment in the earth: and the isles shall wait for his
law.

<span id="xi.i-p9"></span>**4.** Non deficiet, neque frangetur, donec
ponat in terra judicium; et legem ejus insulae expectabunt.

<span id="xi.i-p10"></span>**5.** Thus saith God the LORD, he that
created the heavens, and stretched them out; he that spread forth the
earth, and that which cometh out of it; he that giveth breath unto the
