<span id="xi.i-p11"></span>**5.** Sic dicit Deus *(vel, potens)* Iehova,
creator coelorum, et expandens cos, dilatans terram, et germina ejus;
dans flatum populo in ea habitanti, et spiritum ambulantibus in ea.

<span id="xi.i-p12"></span>**6.** I the LORD have called thee in
