<span id="xi.i-p23"></span>**11.** Exclament desertum et urbes ejus,
villae ubi habitat Kedar; cantent incolae petrae, et e vertice montium
jubilent.

<span id="xi.i-p24"></span>**12.** Let them give glory unto the LORD,
and declare his praise in the islands.

<span id="xi.i-p25"></span>**12.** Dent Iehovae gloriam, et laudem ejus
in insulis annuntient.

<span id="xi.i-p26"></span>**13.** The LORD shall go forth as a mighty
