<span id="xi.i-p27"></span>**13.** Iehova tanquam gigas egredietur, et
sicut praeliator zelum excitabit. Vociferabitur, jubilabit; super
inimicos suos roborabitur.

<span id="xi.i-p28"></span>**14.** I have long time holden my peace; I
have been still, *and* refrained myself: *now* will I cry like a
